<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<sect3 xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" xmlns:db="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" xml:id="ug.reference-guide.reporting.reporters.removed-reporters" version="5.0">
   <title>Removed reporters</title>
   <para>
      There are several reporters that has been removed from PerfCake and has been replaced by others in order
      to improve that particular reporting feature. The following table
      lists the removed reporters and the ones that replaces them.
   </para>
   <table frame="all">
      <title>Removed reporters</title>
      <tgroup cols="2" align="left" colsep="1" rowsep="1">
         <colspec colname="removed-reporter" colwidth="1*"/>
         <colspec colname="replacement" colwidth="1*"/>
         <thead>
            <row>
               <entry>Removed reporter</entry>
               <entry>Replacement</entry>
            </row>
         </thead>
         <tbody>
            <row>
               <entry>AverageThroughputReporter</entry>
               <entry>ThroughputStatsReporter</entry>
            </row>
            <row>
               <entry>ResponseTimeReporter</entry>
               <entry>ResponseTimeStatsReporter</entry>
            </row>
            <row>
               <entry>WindowResponseTimeReporter</entry>
               <entry>ResponseTimeStatsReporter</entry>
            </row>
         </tbody>
      </tgroup>
   </table>
   <para>For the details about the migration of the replaced reporters see <xref linkend="ug.reference-guide.migrating.2-to-3.steps.reporters"/>.</para>
</sect3>
